We are having a issue compiling our java vision code that will be running on the roboRIO. It is using the simple org.opencv.core.Mat and when we deploy the code to the robot we get a unidentified link error. I have found little useful information online on this issue.

Should I be manually installing OpenCV on the coding computer?
Should I try to use JavaCV?
Should I give up and run it on a RasberryPi instead?
Has anybody else had this issue?
